n community at the Plaza de San Pedro in Cartagena,<ref name="Democratic Underground">{{cite web |title=President Obama with Colombian singer Shakira during a ceremony in San Pedro Square, Cartagena -pics |url=http://www.democraticunderground.com/101722259 |publisher=Democratic Underground |accessdate=April 16, 2012 |date=April 15, 2012}}</ref> andvisited the Spanish colonial-era [[Castillo San Felipe de Barajas]].<ref>{{cite news |title=Barack Obama's bodyguards sent home from Colombia summit amid prostitution allegations |url=https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/barackobama/9204309/Barack-Obamas-bodyguards-sent-home-from-Colombia-summit-amid-prostitution-allegations.html |accessdate=April 17, 2012 |newspaper=The Telegraph |date=April 14, 2012 |location=London}}</ref>
